Class ByteComparators.UnsignedComparator

java.lang.Object
com.github.tommyettinger.ds.support.sort.ByteComparators.UnsignedComparator
All Implemented Interfaces:
ByteComparator, Comparator<Byte>
Enclosing class:
ByteComparators
protected static class ByteComparators.UnsignedComparator extends Object implements ByteComparator
A type-specific comparator that compares items in the natural order, but as if they are unsigned (so, all negative items are greater than any non-negative items).
